        "text_dbxCDK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "We're proud to give back to the community that we love so much, and if you have more questions about how you can help more children get better sleep, we encourage you to reach out to us on our <a href=\"https:\/\/5littlemonkeysbed.com\/pages\/contact\">contact page<\/a>. If you haven't yet tried the 5 Little Monkeys mattress, remember: your first 100 nights are risk-free, and if you don't love it, we'll give you a full refund, no questions asked. Give your child the gift of a great night's sleep and try our <a href=\"https:\/\/5littlemonkeysbed.com\/collections\/mattresses-bedding\">revolutionary kids mattress<\/a> today!",
